divs: Sighting Detailsi was stationed aboard the ranger for qual cruse with vf 121 i was assigned to the ready room watch one night and being alone and board i found a book marked classafied. and going throuh it i found one page that showed a cigar craft about 100 feet in the air between two navy vessels they listed the captians and crew all over the photo was stamped offical navy photo i dont know why it was there except in case a piolt saw somthing like it. if i seen this there had to be many piolets that did also the craft had no visable windows it looked almost like rock incrusted had one crude antenna prouding from the bottom. and no visable power. no one believes me but this must be able to veryfiy. thank you all the things you see on tv they want proof if this photo can be retrieved that should do it.
